<p>One player from each group will advance to the next round. Each group plays three games where the player with the highest score gets 3 points, the second gets 1 point, and the last player gets 0 points. The player in the group with the most total points after three games has qualified to the next round (the other two are out). If one player wins the first two games the third game is excluded as the player has already secured the advancement. In the case of an all even result (4p vs. 4p vs. 4p), the player with the highest qualifying rank advances.</p>

