<h3>Round 3</h3>
<p>Again, head-to-head matches, best of three on random machines. The eight winners advance to Round 4.</p>

<h3>Round 4</h3>
<p>Head-to-head matches, best of three random machines. The four winners advance to the Final Round!</p>

<h3>Final Round</h3>
<p>The four players play a 5-ball match on a pre-selected machine. The winner of this match is <span style='font-weight: bold;'>the European Champion 2007</span>!</p>
